<p>And Megan McKenna had another reason to smile on Wednesday night, when she joined a friend for an early birthday meal at London's Roka restaurant.</p>

<p>The TOWIE star, who is set to turn 28 on Saturday, took advantage of the last night bars and eateries can close later than 10pm, as a second lockdown looms.</p>

